itunes:title: DarkHorse Podcast with Brendan O'neill and Bret Weinstein
title: DarkHorse Podcast with Brendan O'neill and Bret Weinstein
description:
Brendan O' neill is an author and host of podcast The Brendan O'neill Show for Spiked. He discusses with Bret the current situation in the US and how it relates to historical events. 

Find Brendan on his podcast: The Brendan O'neill Show 
Find Brendan Instagram: @burntoakby 

Theme Music: Thank you to Martin Molin of Wintergatan for providing us the rights to use their excellent music. 

Support the show (https://www.patreon.com/bretweinstein)
